channel.title: Dell 474
channel.description:
[SIZE=5]Notices[/SIZE]
Dell 474 was a project developed by me and my irl friend, we were aiming to bring 474's back to life, my partner recently quit. a while after my partner contacted me a asking if i would like to start rebuilding a 317 project that we were working on before. i am going to do so. but i thought it would be nice to release the source on which i was working on.
[CODE]MEDIA[/CODE]
[IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/24pwk04.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/2h2dycy.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/5yagec.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/15eg3rn.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/2uzovmc.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/280ukv6.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/24yzi8p.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/260ac1t.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/23u7ep5.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/65yiwz.jpg[/img]
[CODE][SIZE=5]Updates[/SIZE][/CODE] 4/4/10: Ignore system added 3/4/10: Pming system added 3/4/10: Started work on skillcape emotes 3/4/10: Added specials to a few wepons 2/4/10: PvN base added 1/4/10: Started work on player damage 31/3/10: Skill interfaces worked on 30/3/10: Itemdefinition done 28/3/10: Spawning/npc defenition done 26/3/10: A few commands added to help me progress 25/3/10: Npc support added 23/3/10: Started work on basic things 22/3/10: Started work on base
[B]Features:[/B] Pking Great Shops MemberShip Less Lags Tut Island Dueling Castle Wars And Much More
[B]Files:[/B] PotionHandler LevelupHandler TextHandler EventHandler ItemHandler GFXHandler ShopHandler ObjectHandler Anti-Lag BanHandler MembersHandler DialogueHandler RangeHandler MageHandler FoodHandler ParseDialouge TheivingHandler WoodCutting Handler WeaponHandler UpdateHandler MainMenu Handler Teleaport Handler BanMangaer HerbloreHandler EventHandler CraftingHandler LevelUp Handler MagicOnItem Handler TextHandler Custom **** Much More :)
[CODE][SIZE=5]Tools needed[/SIZE][/CODE] Run it on [URL=http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/download.php?file=/technology/epp/downloads/release/galileo/SR2/eclipse-java-galileo-SR2-win32.zip]http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/download.php?file=/technology/epp/downloads/release/galileo/SR2/eclipse-java-galileo-SR2-win32.zip[/URL]
[CODE][SIZE=5]downloads[/SIZE][/CODE] Cache -> Put in c:/ [URL=http://www.mediafire.com/?my2wminhtj2]http://www.mediafire.com/?my2wminhtj2[/URL] Client -> [URL=http://www.mediafire.com/?4kkodlikzlz]http://www.mediafire.com/?4kkodlikzlz[/URL] Source -> [URL=http://www.mediafire.com/?jyzl1m5zntn]http://www.mediafire.com/?jyzl1m5zntn[/URL]
